{"type":"message","id":"903896a1","parentId":"34b743ea","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:16:26.195Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 11:15:00 GMT+8] Exec completed (marine-b, code 0) :: │ │ │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴──────┴─────────┴──────────────┴────────────────┘ FAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq Troubleshooting: h…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ff8e5dc8b4c3091d4bbfea7e3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 11:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54ff8e5dc8b4c3091d4bbfea7e3]\nou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352: 你自己可以给  demo, wechat-assistant 两个飞书机器人 发消息么"}],"timestamp":1773976586193}}
{"type":"message","id":"9192c271","parentId":"903896a1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:16:34.900Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是：我（AI助手）是否可以给两个飞书机器人（demo 和 wechat-assistant）发送消息。\n\n让我检查一下：\n1. 当前用户是通过 feishu（飞书）与我对话\n2. 用户想知道我是否可以给其他飞书机器人发送消息\n\n从工具来看，我有 `message` 工具可以用来发送消息。对于 Feishu 频道，我可以使用 `message` 工具配合 `channel: \"feishu\"` 来发送消息。\n\n但是要给特定的机器人发送消息，我需要知道：\n1. 这些机器人的 chat_id 或 user_id\n2. 或者知道如何定位到它们\n\n查看 message 工具的参数，对于 Feishu：\n- `target`: 可以是 user:open_id 或 chat:chat_id\n- `channel`: \"feishu\"\n\n如果用户想要我给这两个机器人发消息，我需要它们的具体 ID。或者，如果用户是在问\"技术上是否可行\"，那么答案是肯定的 - 我可以使用 message 工具向 Feishu 上的任何用户或聊天发送消息，只要我有目标 ID。\n\n让我先查看当前的 Feishu 应用权限，然后给用户一个明确的回答。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"可以的。我有 `message` 工具可以给飞书用户或群组发送消息。\n\n让我先看看当前有哪些权限："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_AtcjJOYRswFRGQToc1KGZXUl","name":"feishu_app_scopes","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":380,"output":281,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773976586195}}
