{"type":"message","id":"f25d0c60","parentId":"afa199d2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:22:31.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了一个群聊ID：oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\n\n他们说已经在群里@我了，想让我帮忙看看。但我这边看不到群里的具体消息内容，我需要用 message 工具给这个群发送消息。\n\n让我先发送一条消息到群里，看看能否正常发送。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_HAdG3JM6ieIrgsSGDnE3hPbx","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"chat:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","message":"👋 我来测试一下！这个群里有 demo 和 wechat-assistant 两个机器人吗？"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1069,"output":135,"cacheRead":14592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773976946689}}
