{"type":"message","id":"541c3643","parentId":"05d128b6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T03:22:38.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功发送了消息！我可以看到消息ID是 om_x100b54ff99496ca8c32012910b157b2，群聊ID是 oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e。\n\n现在让我给用户确认消息发送成功，并询问具体想让我做什么。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **发送成功！**\n\n我已经往群里发了一条测试消息。我可以正常给这个群发送消息。\n\n你想让我做什么？\n- 给 demo 机器人发特定消息？\n- 给 wechat-assistant 发消息？\n- 或者有什么具体的测试/操作需求？\n\n告诉我就好。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":313,"output":133,"cacheRead":15616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16062,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773976952484}}
