s.md:- 当设置为 `allowlist` 时，`channels.bluebubbles.groupAllowFrom` 控制谁可以在群组中触发。\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/bluebubbles.md:      groupAllowFrom: [\"+15555550123\"],\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/bluebubbles.md:- 使用 `allowFrom` 和 `groupAllowFrom` 确定命令授权。\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/bluebubbles.md:- `channels.bluebubbles.groupAllowFrom`：群组发送者白名单。\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:- `\"allowlist\"` = 仅允许 `groupAllowFrom` 中的群组\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:      groupAllowFrom: [\"oc_xxx\", \"oc_yyy\"],\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:      groupAllowFrom: [\"oc_xxx\"],\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/feishu.md:| `channels.feishu.groupAllowFrom`                  | 群组白名单                        | -                |\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/channels/grammy.md:- **配置选项：** `channels.telegram.botToken`、`channels.telegram.dmPolicy`、`channels.telegram.groups`（allowlist + mention 默认值）、`channels.telegram.allowFrom`、`channels.telegram.groupAllowFrom`、`channels.telegram.groupPolicy`、`channels.telegram.mediaMaxMb`、`channels.telegram.linkPreview`、`channels.telegram.proxy`、`channels.telegram.webhookSecret`、`channels.telegram.webhookUrl`。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":528,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/gateway/configuration-examples.md:      groupAllowFrom: [\"+15555550123\"],\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/gateway/configuration-examples.md:      groupAllowFrom: [\"123456789\"],\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/gateway/configuration.md:对于群组，使用 `channels.whatsapp.groupPolicy` + `channels.