{"type":"message","id":"f1bb0af7","parentId":"348f012e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:54:18.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"你好\"，这是一个简单的问候。我应该回复一下。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋\n\n有什么可以帮你的？比如：\n- 继续配置 demo 和 wechat-assistant 的权限？\n- 解决执行权限问题？\n- 或者其他事情？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":985,"output":55,"cacheRead":23808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773993254448}}
