{"type":"message","id":"d40e0a24","parentId":"121aee77","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:13:02.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，显示了三个 agent：main、demo 和 wechat-assistant。现在用户可以看到完整的 OpenClaw 环境中的 agent 列表了。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"整个 OpenClaw 环境配置了 **3 个 agent**：\n\n| Agent | Workspace | 飞书账号 | 模型 |\n|-------|-----------|----------|------|\n| **main** | `~/.openclaw/workspace` | main (默认) | kimi-coding/k2p5 |\n| **demo** | `~/.openclaw/workspace-demo` | demo | kimi-coding/k2p5 |\n| **wechat-assistant** | `~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant` | wechat-assistant | kimi-coding/k2p5 |\n\n每个 agent 都有独立的 workspace 和 agent 目录，通过飞书不同的账号进行路由。\n\n---\n\n关于 **Tavily API Key**，你想把它配置给哪个 agent 使用？还是全局配置？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":634,"output":196,"cacheRead":28928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29758,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774005178390}}
