{"type":"message","id":"63f6cb6f","parentId":"4d61c051","timestamp":"2026-03-20T15:52:49.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想设置自动提交代码到 GitHub。让我先查看一下文档中关于 Git 自动化或 hooks 的相关配置，以及可能的解决方案。\n\n可能的方式：\n1. 使用 cron 定时任务自动提交\n2. 使用 hooks（webhooks）触发提交\n3. 使用 heartbeat 检查并提交\n4. 使用 git 钩子（pre-commit/post-commit）\n\n让我先查看相关文档。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_EO8KkFLGFuq73CJivHod99ba","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"git\\|github\\|commit\\|push\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ --include=\"*.md\" 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"auto\\|cron\\|hook\\|heartbeat\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":49507,"output":159,"cacheRead":7936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774021959428}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3740cf4","parentId":"63f6cb6f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T15:52:50.042Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_EO8KkFLGFuq73CJivHod99ba","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/credits.md:- **Vincent Koc** ([@vincentkoc](https://github.com/vincentkoc), [@vincent_koc](https://x.com/vincent_koc)) - Agents, Telemetry, Hooks, Security\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/reference/secretref-credential-surface.md:- `hooks.gmail.pushToken`\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/cli/index.md:- `webhooks gmail setup` (requires `--account <email>`; supports `--project`, `--topic`, `--subscription`, `--label`, `--hook-url`, `--hook-token`, `--push-token`, `--bind`, `--port`, `--path`, `--include-body`, `--max-bytes`, `--renew-minutes`, `--tailscale`, `--tailscale-path`, `--tailscale-target`, `--push-endpoint`, `--json`)\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/cli/index.md:- `webhooks gmail setup`（需要 `--account <email>`；支持 `--project`、`--topic`、`--subscription`、`--label`、`--hook-url`、`--hook-token`、`--push-token`、`--bind`、`--port`、`--path`、`--include-body`、`--max-bytes`、`--renew-minutes`、`--tailscale`、`--tailscale-path`、`--tailscale-target`、`--push-endpoint`、`--json`）\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/concepts/agent-workspace.md:git add AGENTS.md SOUL.md TOOLS.md IDENTITY.md USER.md HEARTBEAT.md memory/\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/automation/gmail-pubsub.md:想要自定义端点？使用 `--push-endpoint <url>` 或 `--tailscale off`。\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/automation/gmail-pubsub.md:4. 允许 Gmail push 发布：\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/automation/gmail-pubsub.md:  --member=serviceAccount:gmail-api-push@system.gserviceaccount.com \\\n/usr/loc